item.title: me
item.description: Long Biography Les Vogel, a Staff Engineer for Google Cloud where he led the Serverless team (App Engine, Cloud Run, App Engine Flex), the Java team, and helped launch Cloud Bigtable. He also worked on Google TV, Chromecast and helped launch the YouTube player apis. Before Google: “It turns out Apple has the best Handwriting technology in the world right now.” and “Apple was the first computer company with a low cost WiFi device.
